{"tid":1709050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們還青春 還他們青春","createTime":"2019-11-11T21:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T21:26:20.000Z","uid":199989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f81e8a9a52e969b9c237b0b33f425e41ad250a92","tid":1709050,"uid":199989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:19:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Kc17xJahcY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Kc17xJahcY&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=e8a8ae15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Kc17xJahcY</a><br />\n<br />\n罷工可能會冇咗份工<br />\n但係你知唔知幫你被罷工嘅人會失去咩？<br />\n可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">自由</span>可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">生命</span>可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">貞操</span>可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">健全嘅四肢</span><br />\n一個電話 一張醫生紙就做到嘅嘢點解要佢地咁辛苦走出嚟<br />\n就算真係冇辦法罷（<span style=\"color: red;\">當佢地願意為你賭上十年自由 賭上性命嘅同時，唔該你諗下係咪真係冇辦法可以罷）<br />\n[re</span>d]唔該你諗下今日係地鐵站跪低求人唔好翻工嘅人<br />\n諗番周同學 諗番今日中槍嗰個 你再摸住自己個良心講多一次你罷唔罷到工[/red]<br />\n今日唔好再有人推巴士、清RB得唔得<br />\n當我求下你地，等政府快啲跪低，快啲還番青春比佢地<br />\n佢地仲細 唔應該係由佢地承擔<br />\n係袋住先嘅你地造成今時今日嘅局面<br />\n為左香港嘅未來，罷一星期咁多<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔該你</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnx1eHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqnx1eHA.jpg&h=aadaff8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1f1d4117889e5441261a7aead982aebd2ec2a30","tid":1709050,"uid":199989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:23:13.000Z","msg":"食完早餐就差唔多出發喇"},{"pid":"26f5cab012e27094b2ed19925a9bb7ef27dc771e","tid":1709050,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T21:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！港版64早已發生<br />\n無謂再呃自己出面一切正常</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cha6nZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcha6nZP.jpg&h=ffaebacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">之前山竹：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4ViaBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4ViaBR.jpg&h=c1033d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今日香港：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbH08nJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbH08nJ.png&h=acf9baee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhRdJV4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhhRdJV4.png&h=7a4df7d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhuiY5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhuiY5U.png&h=95045f4c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}